        <item>
            <title>DOCman 3.0 Beta 2 is available</title>
            <pubDate>Wed, 29 Jun 2016 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
            <link>https://www.joomlatools.com/blog/2016/06/docman-30-beta2-is-available/</link>
            <guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.joomlatools.com/blog/2016/06/docman-30-beta2-is-available/</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[
                
                    <img width="800" src="https://www.joomlatools.com/images/blog/2016/docman30-beta2/documents.jpg" alt="" />
                
                <p>We have been working hard since the <a href="/blog/2016/05/docman-30-beta-is-here/">first beta of DOCman 3.0</a> less then two months ago. We fixed 34  bugs and finished all <a href="https://www.joomlatools.com/blog/2016/05/docman-30-beta-is-here/#what-next">promised features</a>.</p>

<!--more-->

<p>Some of the newly added, major features are:</p>

<ul id="markdown-toc">
  <li><a href="#tags" id="markdown-toc-tags">Tags</a></li>
  <li><a href="#custom-ordering" id="markdown-toc-custom-ordering">Custom ordering</a></li>
  <li><a href="#search-and-filter-in-front-end" id="markdown-toc-search-and-filter-in-front-end">Search and filter in front-end</a></li>
  <li><a href="#user-group-management" id="markdown-toc-user-group-management">User group management</a></li>
  <li><a href="#restructured-menu-items" id="markdown-toc-restructured-menu-items">Restructured menu items</a></li>
  <li><a href="#whats-next" id="markdown-toc-whats-next">What’s next?</a></li>
</ul>

<h2 id="tags">Tags</h2>

<p>This has been the most requested feature for years and it’s finally here. You can tag documents and filter front-end menu items based on one or more tags.</p>

<figure>
    <picture>
        
        <source media="(min-width: 400px)" srcset="https://joomlatools.imgix.net/images/blog/2016/docman30-beta2/tags.jpg?w=590&amp;auto=format&amp;q=90,
                https://joomlatools.imgix.net/images/blog/2016/docman30-beta2/tags.jpg?w=885&amp;auto=format&amp;q=90 1.5x,
                https://joomlatools.imgix.net/images/blog/2016/docman30-beta2/tags.jpg?w=1180&amp;auto=format&amp;q=90 2x" />
        
        <source media="(min-width: 0px)" srcset="https://joomlatools.imgix.net/images/blog/2016/docman30-beta2/tags.jpg?w=400&amp;auto=format&amp;q=90,
                https://joomlatools.imgix.net/images/blog/2016/docman30-beta2/tags.jpg?w=600&amp;auto=format&amp;q=90 1.5x,
                https://joomlatools.imgix.net/images/blog/2016/docman30-beta2/tags.jpg?w=800&amp;auto=format&amp;q=90 2x" />
        <img class="image-blog-styled" src="https://joomlatools.imgix.net/images/blog/2016/docman30-beta2/tags.jpg?w=590&amp;auto=format&amp;q=90" alt="List of tags." />
    </picture>
    
    <figcaption><p>List of tags.</p>
</figcaption>
    
</figure>

<h2 id="custom-ordering">Custom ordering</h2>

<p>You can now order documents and categories by dragging and dropping to display them in your preferred order in the front-end.</p>

<p><img src="https://www.joomlatools.com/images/blog/2016/docman30-beta2/ordering.gif" alt="" class="image-blog-styled" /></p>

<h2 id="search-and-filter-in-front-end">Search and filter in front-end</h2>

<p>Finding a document in a long list can sometimes be difficult for your site visitors. You can now enable a search field and additional filters to make it easier to find the desired document.</p>

<figure>
    <picture>
        
        <source media="(min-width: 400px)" srcset="https://joomlatools.imgix.net/images/blog/2016/docman30-beta2/search.jpg?w=590&amp;auto=format&amp;q=90,
                https://joomlatools.imgix.net/images/blog/2016/docman30-beta2/search.jpg?w=885&amp;auto=format&amp;q=90 1.5x,
                https://joomlatools.imgix.net/images/blog/2016/docman30-beta2/search.jpg?w=1180&amp;auto=format&amp;q=90 2x" />
        
        <source media="(min-width: 0px)" srcset="https://joomlatools.imgix.net/images/blog/2016/docman30-beta2/search.jpg?w=400&amp;auto=format&amp;q=90,
                https://joomlatools.imgix.net/images/blog/2016/docman30-beta2/search.jpg?w=600&amp;auto=format&amp;q=90 1.5x,
                https://joomlatools.imgix.net/images/blog/2016/docman30-beta2/search.jpg?w=800&amp;auto=format&amp;q=90 2x" />
        <img class="image-blog-styled" src="https://joomlatools.imgix.net/images/blog/2016/docman30-beta2/search.jpg?w=590&amp;auto=format&amp;q=90" alt="" />
    </picture>
    
    <figcaption>
</figcaption>
    
</figure>

<h2 id="user-group-management">User group management</h2>

<p>DOCman uses group based permissions to make it easier to assign permissions to documents and categories.</p>

<p>A common request was an easy to use interface to assign users to groups from within DOCman. Now you can use the new users view to assign users to groups.</p>

<h2 id="restructured-menu-items">Restructured menu items</h2>

<p>Menu items have been streamlined and made easier to use. We added additional flexibility with 2 new filters: by tag and by owner. You can also set the menu item to only show documents from the logged in user.</p>

<p>Each menu item type (hierarchical, flat, tree) now also supports the same set of layouts: list, table or image gallery.</p>

<figure>
    <picture>
        
        <source media="(min-width: 400px)" srcset="https://joomlatools.imgix.net/images/blog/2016/docman30-beta2/menu-item.jpg?w=590&amp;auto=format&amp;q=90,
                https://joomlatools.imgix.net/images/blog/2016/docman30-beta2/menu-item.jpg?w=885&amp;auto=format&amp;q=90 1.5x,
                https://joomlatools.imgix.net/images/blog/2016/docman30-beta2/menu-item.jpg?w=1180&amp;auto=format&amp;q=90 2x" />
        
        <source media="(min-width: 0px)" srcset="https://joomlatools.imgix.net/images/blog/2016/docman30-beta2/menu-item.jpg?w=400&amp;auto=format&amp;q=90,
                https://joomlatools.imgix.net/images/blog/2016/docman30-beta2/menu-item.jpg?w=600&amp;auto=format&amp;q=90 1.5x,
                https://joomlatools.imgix.net/images/blog/2016/docman30-beta2/menu-item.jpg?w=800&amp;auto=format&amp;q=90 2x" />
        <img class="image-blog-styled" src="https://joomlatools.imgix.net/images/blog/2016/docman30-beta2/menu-item.jpg?w=590&amp;auto=format&amp;q=90" alt="Menu Items are now easier to use and more flexible." />
    </picture>
    
    <figcaption><p>Menu Items are now easier to use and more flexible.</p>
</figcaption>
    
</figure>

<h2 id="whats-next">What’s next?</h2>

<p>We are now stabilizing DOCman 3.0 and preparing it for a stable release. This is where your help can make a great difference. We would love to hear your feedback and issues.</p>

<p>You can <a href="https://support.joomlatools.com/downloads/extras/docman2/12-beta-versions">download the second beta</a> from our Support Center. Already testing the first beta? Just download &amp; install the new version.</p>

<p>Give it a try and let us know!</p>

                ]]>
            </description>
