        <item>
            <title>FILEman 3.0 Beta 2 is available</title>
            <pubDate>Tue, 14 Jun 2016 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
            <link>https://www.joomlatools.com/blog/2016/06/fileman-30-beta2-is-available/</link>
            <guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.joomlatools.com/blog/2016/06/fileman-30-beta2-is-available/</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[
                
                    <img width="800" src="https://www.joomlatools.com/images/blog/2016/fileman30-beta2/files.jpg" alt="" />
                
                <p>Roughly 2 months ago the <a href="https://www.joomlatools.com/blog/2016/03/say-hi-to-fileman-30-beta/">first beta of FILEman 3.0</a> was publicly released introducing some exciting new features. Today we announce the second beta with more new goodies.</p>

<!--more-->

<ul id="markdown-toc">
  <li><a href="#redesigned-user-interface" id="markdown-toc-redesigned-user-interface">Redesigned User Interface</a></li>
  <li><a href="#frontend-management" id="markdown-toc-frontend-management">Frontend management</a></li>
  <li><a href="#docman-attachments-support" id="markdown-toc-docman-attachments-support">DOCman attachments support</a></li>
  <li><a href="#bug-fixes-and-minor-improvements" id="markdown-toc-bug-fixes-and-minor-improvements">Bug fixes and minor improvements</a></li>
  <li><a href="#what-is-next" id="markdown-toc-what-is-next">What is next?</a></li>
</ul>

<h2 id="redesigned-user-interface">Redesigned User Interface</h2>

<p>During the last year we have been redesigning the User Interface (UI) of all of our components. Today FILEman gets released with a new, modern, and responsive UI.</p>

<p>We want our customers to have the best user experience ever on any kind of device. From personal computers with large screens to small smartphones, FILEman is guaranteed to look good and provide a faster and more straightforward experience.</p>

<figure>
    <picture>
        
        <source media="(min-width: 400px)" srcset="https://joomlatools.imgix.net/images/blog/2016/fileman30-beta2/files-full.jpg?w=590&amp;auto=format&amp;q=90,
