<h2 id="frontend-management">Frontend management</h2>

<p>FILEman is now 100% manageable from the frontend. You can now create and delete folders from any of the current available views. Users with create and delete permissions will be able to create and delete folders respectively.</p>

<figure>
    <picture>
        
        <source media="(min-width: 400px)" srcset="https://joomlatools.imgix.net/images/blog/2016/fileman30-beta2/frontend-management.jpg?w=590&amp;auto=format&amp;q=90,
